::Battera::

She felt the tug and followed him. "Ah, that would be fine. Thanks."
She was blushing again. She was getting annoyed with herself.  
Everytime he called her beautiful, she blushed.  She wonderd if there 
was something in her programming to turn that off.

bridge?"
